OL,3,CCost of property in Guernsey
OL,4,Cincreases 54% in last five years
OL,6,FThe average Guernsey property price
OL,7,Fhas gone up 54% in five years, or
OL,8,F7.8% in the last 12 months, according
OL,9,Fto new government statistics.
OL,11,FIt comes after a report earlier this
OL,12,Fyear found that Guernsey housing
OL,13,Fcosts more than anywhere else in
OL,14,FEurope - with the average property
OL,15,Fcosting 16.3x more than the average
OL,16,Fwage.
OL,18,FThe average "local market" property
OL,19,Fin Guernsey cost #647,889 between
OL,20,FJuly and September 2023.
